\c 7
\s UKristu ungumpristi omkhulu njengoMelkizedeki
\p
\v 1 Ngoba uMelkizedeki\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x* lo, inkosi yeSalema\x + Hlab. 76.2. Gen. 33.18.\x*, umpristi kaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke\x + Mark. 5.7.\x*, owahlangabeza uAbrahama mhla ebuya ekubulaleni amakhosi, wasembusisa,
\v 2 uAbrahama laye wamabela okwetshumi kwakho konke\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x*; kuqala uphendulelwa \add ngokuthi\add* inkosi yokulunga, emva kwalokhu beseku\add thiwa\add* futhi inkosi yeSalema\x + Hlab. 76.2. Gen. 33.18.\x*, okuyikuthi inkosi yokuthula\x + Hlab. 76.2.\x*;
\v 3 kalayise, kalanina, kalasendo, kalakuqala kwensuku kumbe ukuphela kwempilo, kodwa esenziwe wafanana leNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 7.28. 1.2.\x*, uhlala engumpristi laphakade\x + 10.1,12,14.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Bonani-ke ukuthi mkhulu kangakanani lo, ngitsho\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x* uAbrahama ukhokho\x + Seb. 2.29.\x* amnika okwetshumi kwezimpango.
\v 5 Lalabo abavela emadodaneni kaLevi\x + Nani 18.21,26. 2 Lan. 31.4,5.\x* abemukela ubupristi balomlayo wokwemukela okwetshumi ebantwini ngokomthetho, okuyikuthi kubafowabo, lanxa bevela ekhalweni lukaAbrahama\x + 7.10.\x*;
\v 6 kodwa yena ongabalelwa osendweni lwabo, wemukela okwetshumi\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x* kuAbrahama, wasembusisa\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x* lowo owayelezithembiso\x + Roma 4.13. Gal. 3.16.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo kungelakuphikwa\x + 6.16.\x* ngitsho \add ukuthi\add*: Omncinyane ubusiswa ngomkhulu.
\v 8 Lapha-ke abantu abafayo bemukela okwetshumi; kodwa lapho \add esemukela lowo\add* okufakazwa\x + 5.6.\x* ngaye ukuthi uyaphila\x + Luka 24.5. Joha. 6.57.\x*.
\v 9 Kungatshiwo-ke, uLevi laye owemukela okwetshumi wanikela okwetshumi ngoAbrahama;
\v 10 ngoba wayesesekhalweni lukayise\x + 7.10.\x*, mhla uMelkizedeki\x + Gen. 14.18-20.\x* emhlangabeza.
\p
\v 11 Ngakho-ke uba kwakukhona ukuphelela\x + 7.18,19. 8.7. 7.25. Gal. 2.21.\x* ngobupristi bukaLevi (ngoba isizwe sanikwa umlayo\x + 8.6.\x* ngaphansi kwabo), kwakusaswelekelani ukuthi kuvele omunye umpristi ngokohlobo lukaMelkizedeki\x + 5.6.\x*, lokungatshiwo ngokwendlela kaAroni?
\v 12 Ngoba uba ubupristi buphendulwa, kuyadingeka ukuthi kube khona lokuphendulwa komlayo.
\v 13 Ngoba lowo okukhulunywa ngaye lezizinto ungowesinye isizwe\x + 7.14.\x*, okungabanga khona kuso owanakekela ilathi.
\v 14 Ngoba kusobala ukuthi iNkosi yethu\x + 7.14.\x*\x + 2.3.\x* yavela\x + Luka 1.78.\x* koJuda\x + Isa. 11.1. Mika 5.2. Mat. 1.3. Luka 3.33. Isam. 5.5.\x*, isizwe uMozisi angakhulumanga lutho ngaso mayelana lobupristi.
\v 15 Njalo kusesobala ngokwengezelelwe kakhulu, uba sekusima omunye umpristi njengokofuzo lukaMelkizedeki,
\v 16 ongenziwanga ngokomthetho wesimiso senyama\x + 9.10.\x*, kodwa ngokwamandla empilo engelakuphela;
\v 17 ngoba ufakaza\x + 2.6.\x* esithi: Wena ungumpristi\x + 7.21. 5.6. Hlab. 110.4.\x* kuze kube nininini ngokohlobo lukaMelkizedeki.
\v 18 Ngoba ukubekwa eceleni komthetho wokuqala kwenziwa ngenxa\x + 7.18,19. 8.7. 7.25. Gal. 2.21.\x*\x + Roma 8.3. Gal. 4.9.\x* yobuthakathaka lokungasizi lutho kwawo;
\v 19 ngoba umlayo\x + 7.18,19. 8.7. 7.25. Gal. 2.21.\x*\x + 9.9; 10.1. Gal 2.16.\x* kawuzanga wenze ulutho luphelele, kodwa uyisingeniso sethemba elingcono\x + 7.22. 6.9; 8.6; 10.34; 11.16,35,40; 12.24.\x*\x + 3.6.\x*, esisondela\x + 4.16. 7.25.\x* ngalo kuNkulunkulu.
\p
\v 20 Njalo okungangokuthi k\add enziwa\add*nga ngaphandle kwesifungo,
\v 21 (ngoba bona baba ngabapristi ngaphandle kwesifungo\f + \fk kwesifungo: \fl kumbe, \fq kukufunga isifungo.\f*, kodwa yena ngesifungo, ngalowo owathi kuye: INkosi yafunga\x + 7.21. 5.6. Hlab. 110.4.\x* njalo kayiyikuzisola\x + Mat. 21.29.\x* \add yathi\add*: Wena ungumpristi kuze kube nininini ngokohlobo lukaMelkizedeki)
\v 22 ngalokho uJesu waba yisibambiso\x + Jobe 17.3.\x* sesivumelwano esingcono\x + 8.6.\x*\x + 7.22. 6.9; 8.6; 10.34; 11.16,35,40; 12.24.\x*\x + Gal. 3.15.\x*.
\v 23 Lalabo babebanengi ababa ngabapristi, ngoba bavinjelwa yikufa ukuthi bahlale njalo;
\v 24 kodwa lo, ngenxa yokuthi uhlala kuze kube phakade\x + 7.21.\x*, ulobupristi obungadluliyo.
\v 25 Ngenxa yalokho laye ulamandla okusindisa ngokupheleleyo\x + 7.11,19. Luka 13.11.\x*\f + \fk ngokupheleleyo: \fl kumbe, \fq ngokulaphakade.\f* abeza kuNkulunkulu ngaye\x + 4.16. 7.25.\x*\x + 11.6.\x*, lokhu ephilela njalo ukubanxusela\x + Roma 8.34.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Ngoba umpristi omkhulu\x + 3.1.\x* onjalo usifanele, ongcwele\x + Isam. 15.4.\x*, ongelacala,\x + Roma 16.18.\x* ongelasici, owehlukaniswe lezoni\x + 4.15.\x*, lowenziwa waphakama kulamazulu\x + 4.14. Efe. 1.20.\x*;
\v 27 ongadingi insuku ngensuku\x + 10.11.\x*, njengabapristi abakhulu, ukunikela imihlatshelo \add esenz\add*ela ezakhe izono kuqala\x + 5.3.\x*, emva kwalokho ezabantu\x + 5.3.\x*; ngoba lokho wakwenza\x + 9.12,14,28; 10.12. Zek. 3.9. Efe. 5.2. Roma 6.10.\x* kanye\x + 10.10.\x* mhla ezinikela yena.
\v 28 Ngoba umlayo uyamisa abantu babe ngabapristi abakhulu, abalobuthakathaka\x + 5.2.\x*; kodwa ilizwi lesifungo\x + 7.21.\x* elalandela umlayo \add lamisa\add* iNdodana\x + 1.2.\x* ephelelisiweyo\x + 5.9.\x* kuze kube nininini.
